*sodium_crypto_box_keypair_from_secretkey_and_publickey*

(PHP 7 >= 7.2.0, PHP 8)

sodium_crypto_box_keypair_from_secretkey_and_publickey â€” Create a unified
keypair string from a secret key and public key

===============================================================================
[ Description ]

  sodium_crypto_box_keypair_from_secretkey_and_publickey(#[\SensitiveParameter]~
  string $secret_key, string $public_key): string~

This function exists to satisfy the API requirements of e.g. crypto_box(). Pass
in one party's secret key and the other's public key, and you will obtain a
"keypair" for your conversation.

===============================================================================
[ Parameters ]

{secret_key}

  Secret key.

{public_key}

  Public key.

===============================================================================
[ Return Values ]

X25519 Keypair.


